contentrichtext.text: '''KOC''' is an abbreviation that can mean: * [[Kings of Convenience]], a Norwegian indie musical group. * [[Knights of Columbus]], a Roman Catholic fraternal organization. * [[Kodiak College]], a college located in Kodiak, Alaska. * [[Kuwait Oil Co.]], one of the biggest oil companies in the world. * [[Korean Olympic Committee]] - represents [[South Korea]] in handling international affairs related to the Olympic Movement. * [[Knights of Cydonia]], a song by the British band [[Muse (band)| Muse]]. * [[Kingdom of Comfort]], a [[Delirious?]] album. * [[Kingdoms of Camelot]], an online game by Kabam ==See also== * [[KoÃ§]], a Turkish name {{disambig}}
